sequenceDiagram
  actor BillingSpecialist as Billing Specialist
  actor CareCoordinator as Care Coordinator
  actor Clinician as Clinician
  actor Nurse as Nurse
  actor Patient as Patient
  participant CarePlanApi as Care Plan API
  participant ChargeApi as Charge API
  participant ClinicalDataApi as Clinical Data API
  participant EncounterApi as Encounter API
  participant OrderEntryApi as Order Entry API
  participant AccountBalance as Account Balance
  participant Appointment as Appointment
  participant CarePlan as Care Plan
  participant Charge as Charge
  participant ClinicalOrder as Clinical Order
  participant Diagnosis as Diagnosis
  participant Encounter as Encounter
  participant Room as Room
  participant VitalSign as Vital Sign
  participant CarePlanScreen as Care Plan Screen
  participant ChargeWorklistScreen as Charge Worklist Screen
  participant DiagnosisScreen as Diagnosis Screen
  participant EncounterWorkspaceScreen as Encounter Workspace
  participant OrderEntryScreen as Order Entry Screen
  participant VitalsScreen as Vitals Screen

  Note over BillingSpecialist,VitalsScreen: Amend Signed Encounter
  Nurse->>EncounterWorkspaceScreen: Amend Signed Encounter
  EncounterWorkspaceScreen->>EncounterApi: Amend Signed Encounter
  activate EncounterApi
  EncounterApi->>Encounter: update
  EncounterApi-->>EncounterWorkspaceScreen: Encounter Workspace
  EncounterWorkspaceScreen-->>Nurse: Encounter Workspace
  deactivate EncounterApi

  Note over BillingSpecialist,VitalsScreen: Complete Appointment
  Nurse->>EncounterWorkspaceScreen: Complete Appointment
  EncounterWorkspaceScreen->>EncounterApi: Complete Appointment
  activate EncounterApi
  rect rgb(245,245,245)
    Note right of EncounterApi: transaction (inferred from FK)
    EncounterApi->>Room: update
    EncounterApi->>Appointment: update
  end
  EncounterApi-->>EncounterWorkspaceScreen: Encounter Workspace
  EncounterWorkspaceScreen-->>Nurse: Encounter Workspace
  deactivate EncounterApi

  Note over BillingSpecialist,VitalsScreen: Create Care Plan
  CareCoordinator->>CarePlanScreen: Create Care Plan
  CarePlanScreen->>CarePlanApi: Create Care Plan
  activate CarePlanApi
  CarePlanApi->>CarePlan: create
  CarePlanApi-->>CarePlanScreen: Care Plan Screen
  CarePlanScreen-->>CareCoordinator: Care Plan Screen
  deactivate CarePlanApi

  Note over BillingSpecialist,VitalsScreen: Create Charge
  BillingSpecialist->>ChargeWorklistScreen: Create Charge
  ChargeWorklistScreen->>ChargeApi: Create Charge
  activate ChargeApi
  ChargeApi->>AccountBalance: update
  ChargeApi->>Charge: create
  ChargeApi-->>ChargeWorklistScreen: Charge Worklist Screen
  ChargeWorklistScreen-->>BillingSpecialist: Charge Worklist Screen
  deactivate ChargeApi

  Note over BillingSpecialist,VitalsScreen: Document Assessment
  Nurse->>DiagnosisScreen: Document Assessment
  DiagnosisScreen->>ClinicalDataApi: Document Assessment
  activate ClinicalDataApi
  rect rgb(245,245,245)
    Note right of ClinicalDataApi: transaction (inferred from FK)
    ClinicalDataApi->>Encounter: update
    ClinicalDataApi->>Diagnosis: create
  end
  ClinicalDataApi-->>DiagnosisScreen: Diagnosis Screen
  DiagnosisScreen-->>Nurse: Diagnosis Screen
  deactivate ClinicalDataApi

  Note over BillingSpecialist,VitalsScreen: Open Encounter
  Nurse->>EncounterWorkspaceScreen: Open Encounter
  EncounterWorkspaceScreen->>EncounterApi: Open Encounter
  activate EncounterApi
  EncounterApi->>Encounter: create
  EncounterApi-->>EncounterWorkspaceScreen: Encounter Workspace
  EncounterWorkspaceScreen-->>Nurse: Encounter Workspace
  deactivate EncounterApi

  Note over BillingSpecialist,VitalsScreen: Place Lab Order
  Clinician->>OrderEntryScreen: Place Lab Order
  OrderEntryScreen->>OrderEntryApi: Place Lab Order
  activate OrderEntryApi
  OrderEntryApi->>ClinicalOrder: create
  OrderEntryApi-->>OrderEntryScreen: Order Entry Screen
  OrderEntryScreen-->>Clinician: Order Entry Screen
  deactivate OrderEntryApi

  Note over BillingSpecialist,VitalsScreen: Record Vitals
  Nurse->>VitalsScreen: Record Vitals
  VitalsScreen->>ClinicalDataApi: Record Vitals
  activate ClinicalDataApi
  rect rgb(245,245,245)
    Note right of ClinicalDataApi: transaction (inferred from FK)
    ClinicalDataApi->>Encounter: update
    ClinicalDataApi->>VitalSign: create
  end
  ClinicalDataApi-->>VitalsScreen: Vitals Screen
  VitalsScreen-->>Nurse: Vitals Screen
  deactivate ClinicalDataApi

  Note over BillingSpecialist,VitalsScreen: Sign Encounter
  Nurse->>EncounterWorkspaceScreen: Sign Encounter
  EncounterWorkspaceScreen->>EncounterApi: Sign Encounter
  activate EncounterApi
  EncounterApi->>Encounter: update
  EncounterApi-->>EncounterWorkspaceScreen: Encounter Workspace
  EncounterWorkspaceScreen-->>Nurse: Encounter Workspace
  deactivate EncounterApi

